onto the Vampire Hunter,

49:29.092 --> 49:31.720
and then the sunlight
has come through here

49:31.803 --> 49:33.555
and burned Petyr alive.

49:34.306 --> 49:37.643
I think this is just a table leg,
which is sanded down.

49:37.726 --> 49:39.436
Do you think he hand-sanded that or...

49:39.519 --> 49:41.855
- Yes. Imagine that stuck in your...
- Your leg.

49:42.439 --> 49:44.524
VIAGO: It's quite
shocking down here, Nick.

49:44.608 --> 49:47.903
Look, here's our sweet Petyr

49:47.986 --> 49:50.113
- burned to a sizzle.
- NICK: Oh! Fuck. Yeah.

49:50.197 --> 49:51.466
VLADISLAV: I can't figure out this.

49:51.490 --> 49:52.616
