49:52.699 --> 49:54.427
- Is this his front or his back?
- NICK: Oh, who's this guy?

49:54.451 --> 49:57.120
VIAGO: Look at his
bloody head on back-to-front.

49:57.204 --> 49:58.264
Twist it the other way, the other way.

49:58.288 --> 49:59.289
VLADISLAV: This way.

49:59.373 --> 50:01.958
VIAGO: See who this guy is here.

50:03.418 --> 50:05.712
- Hmm. Typical macho type.
- Yuck!

50:05.796 --> 50:06.797
Hideous.

50:06.880 --> 50:08.215
NICK: Oh, shit.

50:09.299 --> 50:10.926
I know that guy, actually.

50:11.009 --> 50:12.135
VLADISLAV: You know him?

50:12.219 --> 50:13.637
- Yeah.
- VIAGO: What?

50:13.720 --> 50:15.389
I saw him the other night in town.

50:16.139 --> 50:17.808
- Told him I was a vampire.
- VIAGO: What?

50:17.891 --> 50:20.143
I thought he was joking.
